Package: rsegregation
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Empirical Measures of Segregation
Version: 0.2.6
Author: Arthur Gailes
Maintainer: Arthur Gailes <arthurgailes@berkeley.edu>
Description: Provides functions for several empirical measures of racial segregation within a tidy framework.
    Includes divergence, entropy, dissimilarity, exposure, isolation, and location quotient.
    This packages was inspired by work done by the Othering & Belonging Institute at UC Berkeley.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0),
Imports:
  dplyr(>= 1.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
